# GitHub personal access token (classic or fine-grained).
# Create one at: https://github.com/settings/tokens
# Scopes needed: public_repo (or read-only repo access for fine-grained tokens)
#
# Raises API rate limit from 60 → 5,000 requests/hour and fetches
# DETAILS.md plus repo metadata in project detail sheets.
VITE_GITHUB_TOKEN=
